  "texts": [
    "Additionally, the threshold τ server effectively balances the losses caused by the misleading and ambiguous knowledge, as indicated by the inequalities 2 À τ server ≤ k ĥ* ðxÞ À h * proxy ðxÞk 1 and k ĥ* proxy ðxÞ À h * proxy ðxÞk 1 ≤ τ server.",
    "This property aligns with the empirical results presented in Fig. 6.",
    "The proposed mechanism for selectively sharing knowledge and its associated thresholds τ client, τ server might alter the distributions D proxy, Dproxy, thus influencing the empirical risk, the minimum combined loss, the G k -distance, and the probabilities p ð1Þ proxy,p ð2Þ proxy in Theorem 2.",
    "A more comprehensive and rigorous analysis of these effects is left to our future work.",
    "Nature Communications | (2024) 15:349"
  ]
